!! [[TiddlyTools/Time/WorldClocks]]
<<<
''Displays a set of analog and digital clocks for a set of selected places''
<br>Requires: [[TiddlyTools/Time/Clocks]], [[TiddlyTools/Time/Places]], [[TiddlyTools/Time/Ticker]], [[TiddlyTools/Time/action-timeout.js]]
<br>Optional: [[TiddlyTools/Time/Places/Summer]], [[TiddlyTools/Time/Setup]], <$link to=<<tt_time_config>>/>

* The clocks show the current time from your computer's system settings, plus the local time for each selected place.
* The digital clocks also display the [[timezone offset|https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_UTC_time_offsets]], using `-12:00` through `+12:00`, where the number is the hours and minutes offset from [[UTC|https://www.timeanddate.com/time/aboututc.html]].
* Press <<button "Select places...">> to view a popup with available places to display:
** Click on the heading list to choose one or more sets of places. Use <kbd>ctrl-click</kbd> or <kbd>shift-click</kbd> to select multiple items.
** Set or clear checkboxes to show or hide clocks for individual places.
** ''<input type=checkbox/> select all'' selects all checkboxes. ''<input type=checkbox checked=checked/> clear all'' resets all checkboxes.
** <<button {{$:/core/images/edit-button}} tc-btn-invisible>> edits the first selected set of places (see [[TiddlyTools/Time/Places]] below).
** <<button {{$:/core/images/clone-button}} tc-btn-invisible>> copies the selected individual places to a new set (see [[TiddlyTools/Time/Places]] below).
** <<button {{$:/core/images/delete-button}} tc-btn-invisible>> deletes the first selected set of places. You will be asked to confirm before deletion.
* Press <<button "{{$:/core/images/options-button}}">> to view a popup with display options:
** You can adjust the size of the analog and digital clocks. Choose a percentage between 50% and 200% (default is 100%).
** You can choose to show/hide the digital clocks and set the time/date format used by the digital clocks (see [[TiddlyWiki Date Format codes|https://tiddlywiki.com/#DateFormat]]).
